{"tid":1095034,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有個有錢仔同學想曬命但。。。","createTime":"2019-04-06T17:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T03:55:18.000Z","uid":8550,"like":653,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0d47b68d12160c1d12bab9a37bb8ac8d66e776","tid":1095034,"uid":8550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:38:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同學=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我：係呢 話說識咗咁耐都未知你住邊頭<br />\n<br />\n同學：等你問呢句好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我屋企都算中產嘅 daddy 就喺養和三樓做精神科醫生 媽咪就做律師 月入都160k<br />\n<br />\n我：嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同學：不過Daddy 話平時返工好攰 所以上個月全家<br />\n搬咗去養和醫院附近住 仲要full pay <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過你個新界牛屎仔都應該未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我：乜咁啱 原來你都係住養和嗰頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我住養和咋嘛 仲要住低層 三樓 得下咪過嚟我度飲杯茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n跟著個同學就好快咁跑走咗......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都未同佢講我係住養和李樹芬院嘅三樓佢就跑走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁佢又點識上嚟搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我懷疑佢一定係知道我仲rich過佢所以覺得冇面先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa14c6ab2aafe8f3a973b4a779a98dc3